                                    </span>
                                    <br/>&amp;nbsp; ตัวอักษร</td>
                                    <td class="text-right" style="border-top: 1px solid black!important;border-left: 1px solid black!important;border-right: 1px solid black!important;;border-bottom: 1px solid black!important;"><t t-esc="'{0:,.2f}'.format(o.amount)"/>&amp;nbsp;</td>
                                   </tr>                                                                       
                                  </tbody>
                            </table>
                            <br/>
                            <table style="width:100%;font-size:20px" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
